+```
+Create a Filipino Food quiz game featuring three main difficulty levels ( easy, medium, and hard) to challenge players with common, regional and lesser-known Filipino dishes. The game will include image-base questions where players identify dishes from pictures, and feature fun sound effect like chimes for correct answers and buzzers for wrong ones. Players will receive short food facts after each question and have their score displayed at the end. The UI will be colorful and playful, with friendly, encouraging tone to engage users while they learn about Filipino cuisine. 
